# 拦截阿里系窃取隐私/上报真实IP的API
host-suffix, guide-acs.taobao.com, reject
host-suffix, h-adashx.ut.taobao.com, reject
host-suffix, adashx.m.taobao.com, reject
host-suffix, amdc.m.taobao.com, reject
host, dns.alidns.com, reject

# 闲鱼专属规则 - 代理这些请求以伪装定位IP
# 注意：请将下方的 "Proxy" 替换为您实际使用的节点或策略组名称（例如 "US"、"Japan" 等）
host-keyword, acs.m.goofish.com, Proxy

# 闲鱼及淘宝共用IP段 (走代理)
ip-cidr, 59.82.58.0/24, Proxy
ip-cidr, 59.82.66.0/24, Proxy
ip-cidr, 59.82.84.0/24, Proxy
ip-cidr, 59.82.122.0/24, Proxy
ip-cidr, 59.82.121.0/24, Proxy
ip-cidr, 59.82.133.0/24, Proxy
ip-cidr, 203.119.146.0/24, Proxy
ip-cidr, 203.119.204.0/24, Proxy
